##NLP   

This is based on [Mark Watson's](http://www.markwatson.com/) pos tagger and using JavaScript. The JavaScript library can be downloaded at [jspos](http://code.google.com/p/jspos/). This includes a compressed lexicon provided by  Toby Rahilly.

